1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top">377/997 (37.8)</td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="left" valign="top">In the past 24 hours, how many times have you washed your hands with soap and water (not including baths, showers, or washing up)?:</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="left" valign="top">&#x02003;0 to 4</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top">229/990 (23.0)</td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="left" valign="top">&#x02003;5 to 9</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top">352/990 (35.6)</td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="left" valign="top">&#x02003;10 to 14</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top">206/990 (20.8)</td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="left" valign="top">&#x02003;15 to 19</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top">65/990 (6.6)</td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="left" valign="top">&#x02003;&#x02265;20</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top">138/990 (13.9)</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id="largeobj_idm139625095257872" class="largeobj-link align_right" style="display: none"><a target="object" href="/pmc/articles/PMC2714687/table/tbl1/?report=objectonly">Open in a separate window</a></div><div class="tblwrap-foot"><p id="__p17">*Behavioural changes classified as avoidance.</p><p id="__p18">&#x02020;Behavioural changes classified as recommended.</p></div></div></div><div id="__sec6" class="sec"><h3 id="__sec6title">Perceived efficacy of behaviours</h3><p id="__p19" class="p p-first">Six items assessed whether participants believed that a specific action reduced their risk of catching swine flu, with possible response options being strongly agree (scored as 5), tend to agree (4), neither agree nor disagree (3), tend to disagree (2), or strongly disagree (1). Table 2<a href="/pmc/articles/PMC2714687/table/tbl2/" target="table" class="fig-table-link figpopup" rid-figpopup="tbl2" rid-ob="ob-tbl2" co-legend-rid=""><span style="position: relative;text-decoration:none;">&#x200B;<span class="figpopup-sensitive-area" style="left: -0.5em;">2</span></span><span></span></a> gives the wording for these questions.</p><!--table ft1--><!--table-wrap mode="anchored" t5--><div class="table-wrap table anchored whole_rhythm" id="tbl2"><h3>Table 2</h3><!--caption a7--><div class="caption"><p id="__p20">&#x02002;Perceived efficacy of various behavioural responses to swine flu. Values are numbers (percentages) of participants</p></div><div data-largeobj="" data-largeobj-link-rid="largeobj_idm139625138630832" class="xtable"><table frame="hsides" rules="groups" class="rendered small default_table"><thead><tr><th colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="left" valign="bottom">Question</th><th colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="bottom">Strongly agree</th><th colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="bottom">Tend to agree</th><th colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="bottom">Neither agree nor disagree</th><th colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="bottom">Tend to disagree</th><th colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="bottom">Strongly disagree</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="left" valign="top">I believe that . . . reduces your risk of catching swine flu:</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top"></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top"></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top"></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top"></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="left" valign="top">&#x02003;Reducing the number of people you meet over a day</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top">162/975 (16.2)</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" align="center" valign="top">303/975 (31.1)</td><td colspan="1" rowsp